{"tid":1576951,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"你同我一樣憤怒嗎？悲傷嗎？內疚嗎？無力嗎？","createTime":"2019-09-17T12:53:12.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-17T12:57:55.000Z","uid":274607,"like":4,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"b9ec489faf69818237a20af04805e9f673f6c60d","tid":1576951,"uid":274607,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-17T12:53:12.000Z","msg":"各位手足，<br />\n<br />\n運動至今過了 100 日鳥，每日睇新聞、連登、tg，每星期夢遊，心情好似坐過山車咁。你同我一樣憤怒嗎？悲傷嗎？內疚嗎？無力嗎？<br />\n<br />\n憤怒，係望住警黑咁虐打義士，望住政府指鹿為馬，望住藍絲是非不分。 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n悲傷，係睇住義士被打至頭破血流，被控暴動，隨時要坐十年。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n內疚，係望住人地既付出，覺得自己做得唔夠，但又因為種種原因，難以付出更多。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n無力，係做左咁撚多野，都好似爭取唔到五大訴求，阻止唔到香港沈淪。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n仲有好多好多好多野：害怕、擔心⋯⋯<br />\n<br />\n其實除左唱歌，十點鳩嗌，仲有一樣野可以做。<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\"><br />\n很重要所以講三次<br />\n喊出黎。<br />\n喊出黎。<br />\n喊出黎。</span></span></strong><br />\n<br />\n唔好收收埋埋，會谷壞身體的。<br />\n因為情緒唔抒發，會埋藏係身體內，唔會自己走左去。<br />\n<br />\n我大喊出黎，好左好多。<br />\n訓一覺，抖夠，繼續抗爭。<br />\n所以想同各位手足分享下我既方法 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n歡迎心理學 JJ 補充後面既理論"},{"pid":"373885a5db7a43f3dd1519d7a5a6a2b69fdcba8e","tid":1576951,"uid":93962,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-17T12:53:35.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"a27fdd5f06771c653241d301bde7d5df21d0d2a8","tid":1576951,"uid":230725,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-17T12:54:03.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"2404349d75fe49f60d74febffa3dbe03be53a92e","tid":1576951,"uid":160916,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-17T12:54:07.000Z","msg":"喊咗好多次了<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5e88f74ecd7ae9c75d2b074a1d51e4e0794d04ea","tid":1576951,"uid":293254,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-17T12:55:18.000Z","msg":"仲有一班港豬 義士們不停付出 班港豬仲去吃喝玩樂"},{"pid":"734cf85c8f7c021044987deedb4fe9398afff56a","tid":1576951,"uid":269202,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-17T12:56:58.000Z","msg":"是的,"},{"pid":"854c3deb6f1441a6e9bd0cdbfa03184d511a5d17","tid":1576951,"uid":228437,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-17T12:57:12.000Z","msg":"【極重要】（被？）自殺的失蹤人士<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1576845\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1576845</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"2ca916b11e0576581ea84885626ae450be2912af","tid":1576951,"uid":234089,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-17T12:57:55.000Z","msg":"推推推推推推<br />\n<br />\n五大訴求 缺一不可"}]}